        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *+1 striking kukri* has a crimson blade that shimmers eerily in bright light. On a critical hit, the kukri deals 1d8 persistent bleed damage. If the target didn't already have persistent bleed damage when you scored the critical hit, you also gain 1d8 temporary Hit Points for 1 minute.",
